	<h1>Terms &amp; Privacy Policy</h1>

	<div class="section">
		<p>The <em>CV Maker</em> Privacy Policy statement discloses the privacy practices employed by <em>CV Maker</em>. To learn more about <em>CV Maker</em>'s privacy policy please read the information listed below. The protection of privacy and the safeguarding of our Clients personal information is our highest precedence. Please view the following Privacy Statement which clearly explains how <em>CV Maker</em> collects, processes, stores and protects your information. By using this website or opening an account, you hereby give <em>CV Maker</em> your consent to such processing, collection, storage and use of personal information by <em>CV Maker</em> as explained below.  
		This policy covers how <em>CV Maker</em> treats personal information that we may collect and receive, including information related to your past use of our services and products. Identification like your name, address, email address, or phone number, and that which is not otherwise publicly available is considered to be personal information. By no means does this policy apply to the practices of companies that <em>CV Maker</em> doesn't control or own or to individuals that <em>CV Maker</em> does not manage. 
		</p>
		<p><em>CV Maker</em> allows people to generate resumes online based on the data provided by them. </p>
	</div>
	
	<div class="section">
		<h2>Changes and Terms to this Privacy Statement</h2>
		<p><em>CV Maker</em> reserves the right to modify this agreement at any time. Your continued use of <em>CV Maker</em> following any such modification constitutes your agreement to be bound by and your acceptance of the agreement as so modified. Your continual use of the site indicates your acquiesce to any changes and constitutes your agreement to be bound by and your acceptance of the agreement as so modified. If you have any questions or feedback regarding this policy, please contact info&#064;cvmkr.com and make sure to put “<em>CV Maker</em> Privacy Policy” in the subject line of the email. You are hereby responsible for reviewing this Privacy Policy sporadically to make certain that you are aware of any changes to it. </p>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<h2>Collection and use of user information</h2>
		<p><em>CV Maker</em> collects personal information (name, contact information such as e-mail, phone, employment history, education records, and other information pertaining to career and employment history or personal profile) from its users <strong>solely</strong> for the purpose of generating their resumes, except as required by (a) federal, state, or international law, (b) subpoena, or court order, (c) the user's written consent, or (d) any other legitimate concerns, such as, ethical conflicts and genuine emergencies. <em>CV Maker</em> will not sell, share, or rent the user information to any third party. No personal information or user data is retained after deletion by the respective owner, where <em>deletion</em> is an easily accessible, explicit option provided to the user by <em>CV Maker</em>. If an entity wholly acquires <em>CV Maker</em>, the company and product, including IP, technology, rights, brand, user, resume, and other data, all liabilities, including security, privacy, and data protection shall be transferred to the entity from <em>CV Maker</em>, the company, and its proprietors.</p>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<h2>Information Disclosure</h2>
		<p><em>CV Maker</em> doesn't split, sell, share, or rent personal information about you with other people or non-affiliated companies apart from providing service's you may have requested, with your authorization, or under the following circumstance: </p>
		<p><em>CV Maker</em> reserves the right to transport information about you and your use of this website in the occurrence of a transfer of rights of <em>CV Maker</em>, such as a takeover, acquisition, or merger with another company. </p>

		<h3>Publishing resumes online</h3>
		<p><em>CV Maker</em> makes your resumes / CVs publically visible via a unique URL <strong>if and only if</strong>
		you explicitly set the status of a resume to <em>Publish</em> in its <em>Share</em> options. By default, all resumes are
		set to <em>Unpublish</em>, therefore private. Resumes explicitly published by you may be indexed by 3rd party search engines
		and sites and made available on their websites.
		<em>CV Maker</em> is neither responsible nor liable for where your resume content appears after you have made it public.</p>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<h2>Cookies</h2>
		<p>Cookies are small pieces of information stored on the user's computer. <em>CV Maker</em> may access and set cookies on your computer. The cookie allows the <em>CV Maker</em> system to identify a user as a registered member and save some preferences that have nothing to do with a user's personal information. A small piece of encrypted data is stored in the cookie when a user logs in and this helps <em>CV Maker</em> identify the user later and automatically signs him/her in without the need of any manual action from the user. This cookie, in no way exposes any sensitive information.
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<h2>Correspondences</h2>
		<p><em>CV Maker</em> may contact its users from time to time to notify of important changes on the system, technical updates etc. <em>CV Maker</em> may also store correspondences from its users for tracking purposes, and these won't be shared/sold or rented to any thirdparty except as requred by (a) federal, state or international law, (b) subpoena or court order, (c) the user's written consent or other legit, genuine and ethical emergencies. </p>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<h2>Disclaimer</h2>
		<p>Except as expressly provided otherwise in a written agreement between you and <em>CV Maker</em>, the online tool, resumes and document generated for users, and any materials included therein are provided "as is" and without warranties of any kind, either expresses or implied. To the fullest extent permissible pursuant to applicable law, <em>CV Maker</em> disclaims all warranties, express or implied, including, but not limited to, implied warranties of merchantability or fitness for a particular purpose, or the warranty of non-infringement. Without limiting the foregoing, <em>CV Maker</em> does not warrant that the functions contained in the community or available through the community will be uninterrupted or error-free, that defects will be corrected, or that the community or the server that makes it available are free of viruses or other harmful components. <em>CV Maker</em> does not warrant or make any representations regarding the use or the results of the use of the materials on the community in terms of their correctness, accuracy, reliability, or otherwise. You (and not <em>CV Maker</em>) assume the entire cost of all necessary servicing, repair, or correction. Applicable law may not allow the omission of implied warranties, so the above omission may not apply to you. </p>
		<p>Under no circumstances, including, but not limited to, negligence, shall <em>CV Maker</em> be liable for any special or consequential damages that result from the use of, or the inability to use, the community or any service provided therein, even if the <em>CV Maker</em> or a Company authorized representative has been advised of the possibility of such damages. Applicable law may not allow the limitation or omission of liability for incidental or consequential damages, so the above limitation or omission may not apply to you. No advice or information, whether written or oral, obtained by you from <em>CV Maker</em> or from or through the community shall create any warranty not expressly stated in these terms of use. Notwithstanding the provisions of any applicable laws, it is hereby agreed that in no event shall the <em>CV Maker</em>’s total liability to you for all damages, losses, and causes of action (whether in contract, tort (including, but not limited to, carelessness) or otherwise) exceed the amount paid by you, if any, for purchasing any materials, services or products.</p>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<h2>No guarantees or warranties</h2>
		<p>Due to technical, legal and practical limitations, <em>CV Maker</em> cannot warrant and does not guarantee the non-disclosure of the user's private/personal information and data in ways not described in this privacy policy. <em>CV Maker</em> may disclose information to government authorities or third parties under certain circumstances, or third parties may unlawfully intercept or access private data or communications. As the user, you authorize <em>CV Maker</em> to disclose any information about you to law enforcement or other government officials/bodies as <em>CV Maker</em>, in its sole discretion, believes necessary, prudent or appropriate, in connection with an investigation of fraud, intellectual property infringement, or other activity that is illegal or may expose <em>CV Maker</em> to legal liability.</p>
	</div>
